Only in silence the word,
only in dark the light,

4
00:00:17,417 --> 00:00:20,047
only in dying life:

5
00:00:20,754 --> 00:00:23,684
bright the hawk's flight
on the empty sky.

6
00:00:24,424 --> 00:00:27,054
.
